w and meta-analysis. <em>Eur Radiol</em> 2023;33(4):2792–2799.</div><div class="external-links"><div class="core-xlink-crossref"><a href="https://doi.org/10.1007/s00330-022-09258-5">Crossref</a></div><div class="core-xlink-pubmed"><a href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/36449058/">PubMed</a></div><div class="core-xlink-google-scholar"><a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=Radiological+predictive+factors+of+transmural+intestinal+necrosis+in+acute+mesenteric+ischemia%3A+systematic+review+and+meta-analysis&amp;author=Y+Zeng&amp;author=F+Yang&amp;author=X+Hu&amp;author=F+Zhu&amp;author=W+Chen&amp;author=W+Lin&amp;publication_year=2023&amp;journal=Eur+Radiol&amp;pages=2792-2799&amp;doi=10.1007%2Fs00330-022-09258-5&amp;pmid=36449058">Google Scholar</a></div></div></div></div></div><div role="listitem" data-has="label"><div class="label">9.</div><div id="r9" class="citations"><div class="citation"><div class="citation-content">Theodore S, Xia T, Saillant N. Intestinal Ischemia: Etiology and Foundational Concepts. <em>NEJM Evid</em> 2024;3(3):EVIDra2300266.</div><div class="external-links"><div class="core-xlink-crossref"><a href="https://doi.org/10.1056/EVIDra2300266">Crossref</a></div><div class="core-xlink-pubmed"><a href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/38411445/">PubMed</a></div><div class="core-xlink-google-scholar"><a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=Intestinal+Ischemia%3A+Etiology+and+Foundational+Concepts&amp;author=S+Theodore&amp;author=T+Xia&amp;author=N+Saillant&amp;publication_year=2024&amp;journal=NEJM+Evid&amp;pages=EVIDra2300266&amp;doi=10.1056%2FEVIDra2300266&amp;pmid=38411445">Google Scholar</a></div></div></div></div></div><div role="listitem" data-has="label"><div class="label">10.</div><div id="r10" class="citations"><div class="citation"><div class="citation-content">Furukawa A, Kanasaki S, Kono N, et al. CT Diagnosis of Acute Mesenteric Ischemia from Various Causes. <em>AJR Am J Roentgenol</em> 2009;192(2):408–