+Jacobs&amp;publication_year=2003&amp;journal=AJR+Am+J+Roentgenol&amp;pages=733-736&amp;doi=10.2214%2Fajr.180.3.1800733&amp;pmid=12591685">Google Scholar</a></div></div></div></div></div><div role="listitem" data-has="label"><div class="label">74.</div><div id="r74" class="citations"><div class="citation"><div class="citation-content">Wiesner W, Mortelé KJ, Glickman JN, Ji H, Ros PR. Pneumatosis Intestinalis and Portomesenteric Venous Gas in Intestinal Ischemia. <em>AJR Am J Roentgenol</em> 2001;177(6):1319–1323.</div><div class="external-links"><div class="core-xlink-crossref"><a href="https://doi.org/10.2214/ajr.177.6.1771319">Crossref</a></div><div class="core-xlink-pubmed"><a href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/11717075/">PubMed</a></div><div class="core-xlink-google-scholar"><a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=Pneumatosis+Intestinalis+and+Portomesenteric+Venous+Gas+in+Intestinal+Ischemia&amp;author=W+Wiesner&amp;author=KJ+Mortel%C3%A9&amp;author=JN+Glickman&amp;author=H+Ji&amp;author=PR+Ros&amp;publication_year=2001&amp;journal=AJR+Am+J+Roentgenol&amp;pages=1319-1323&amp;doi=10.2214%2Fajr.177.6.1771319&amp;pmid=11717075">Google Scholar</a></div></div></div></div></div><div role="listitem" data-has="label"><div class="label">75.</div><div id="r75" class="citations"><div class="citation"><div class="citation-content">Duron VP, Rutigliano S, Machan JT, Dupuy DE, Mazzaglia PJ. Computed Tomographic Diagnosis of Pneumatosis Intestinalis: Clinical Measures Predictive of the Need for Surgical Intervention. <em>Arch Surg</em> 2011;146(5):506–510.</div><div class="external-links"><div class="core-xlink-crossref"><a href="https://doi.org/10.1001/archsurg.2011.95">Crossref</a></div><div class="core-xlink-pubmed"><a href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/21576602/">PubMed</a></div><div class="core-xlink-google-scholar"><a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=Computed+Tomographic+Diagnosis+of+Pneumatosis+Intestinalis%3A+Clinical+Measure